<number box="[558,613,736,760]" pageId="8" pageNumber="49" value="9.5" valueMax="11.0" valueMin="8.0">8–11</number>
additional teeth each (Fig. 
<number box="[919,951,736,760]" pageId="8" pageNumber="49" value="68.0">68</number>
